{
  "title": "关闭Centos7的防火墙",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在Centos7 64下部署RocketMQ，但客户端发送信息失败，在nameserver上安装了个tomcat，在nameserver上浏览tomcat没问题，在其他设备上就打不开，那肯定是防火墙问题了，先关掉。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Centos7的防火墙用firewalld.service，而不是iptable……</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;systemctl stop firewalld.service &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;关闭防火墙</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;systemctl disable firewalld.service &nbsp;禁止开机启动防火墙</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 而如果是其他系统，关闭iptables的命令是：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; systemctl disable iptables.service&nbsp;</p>"
    }
  ]
}